Jade is Leboeuf's eldest child with first wife Beatrice. 
Her boyfriend Stephane Rodrigues took part in the Secret Story reality show, while her brother Hugo is a comedian. 
Former Blues fan favourite Frank is now married to actress Chrislaure Nollet. He works as a pundit, and has taken part in French reality TV show Koh-Lanta.
